MOST IMME

GOVERNMENT OF INDIA (BHARAT SARKAR)
CABINET SECRETARIAT (MANTRIMANDAL SACHIVALAYA)
New Delhi, the 26th June, 2012
--- --
The undersigned is directed to say that with effect from the 26th June, 2012:-
Shri Pranab Mukherjee relinquished the charge of the office of the Minister of Finance;
(ii)
the Prime Minister assumed the charge of the office of the Minister of Finance;
(ii)
Shri Virbhadra Singh relinquished the charge of the office of the Minister of Micro, Small
and Medium Enterprises; and
(iv)
Sciences assumed the additional charge of the office of the Minister of Micro, Small and
Medium Enterprises.
Shri Vilasrao Deshmukh, Minister of Science and Technology and Minister of Earth
(K.L. Shàrma)
